name: heart brooch
description:
Soft, embellished layers of loveliness.  Makes a winter coat or sweater festive and arty.
It is extremely light-in-weight, made from felt, vinyl, seedbeads and a handmade glass button. It measures 3" across and has a bar-style finding.

name: knotted bracelet - winter colors
description:
Neutral and turquoise ingredients make this bracelet wearable with everything!
It is made from my handmade glass beads and button, as well as vintage glass beads, and is knotted with linen and floss.
It is for a 6-1/2" wrist, a medium-sized woman.

name: elegant party earrings - amber
description:
Neutral colors and a fancy, long shape. Fun as well as elegant.
They hang 3" from the top of the loop. 
Handmade glass beads, vintage beads, chain and parts, sterling beads & findings.

name: tinkerbell drops - purple & orange
description:
These cute little earrings are perfect for a young person on your list or those who like more diminutive ear-wear. They still have all the sass of my other jewelry though!
They hang 1-1/2" in length from the top of the earwire and the flower is 1" in diameter. Sterling findings.

name: fruit salad necklace
description:
A signature Stephanie necklace.
Big, bold beads in an unbelievably light-weight piece.
There a few handmade, hollow glass beads, horn, recycled glass, coral and resin beads. Strung on Softflex with a vintage glass button.
19" long, for a medium or large neck.

name: alligator totem
description:
A little talisman to beckon good energy to the wearer.
The pendant is 1-1/2" tall and the alligator is 2" wide. The ribbon is washed silk.

name: pretty flower necklace
description:
A sweet and subtle strand of ink-blue beads with a stunning flower pendant in the center.
Made from my own lampwork beads, a pretty little button and seed beads.  It's strung on Softflex wire.
It measures 20" in length.  The flower pendant is 1-7/8" wide.

name: lilac bird earrings
description:
They measure 1-1/4" in length from the top of the loop and the birds are 1-1/4" long.
Handmade glass beads, seed beads and sterling findings.

name: tinkerbell drops - pink & green
description:
These cute little earrings are perfect for a young person on your list or those who like more diminutive ear-wear. They still have all the sass of my other jewelry though!
They hang 1-1/2" in length from the top of the earwire and the flower is 1" in diameter. Sterling findings.

name: starfish brooch
description:
Happy colors will brighten up a winter wardrobe.
Measures 2" in diameter. Made from Bullseye glass. Pad & post-style finding.

name: flower hoops - blue & green
description:
These little lovelies are so simple and easy to wear.
The hoops are 5/8" in diameter and the flower is 1" in diameter.
The hoops are sterling silver.

name: ocean colors bracelet
description:
This bracelet is made from the funkiest combination of my handmade beads, all in colors of the ocean.
It measures 8" long, for a large size wrist.
It is made from my handmade glass beads and glass accent beads and strung on Softflex.

name: frida flower brooch
description:
This brooch would liven up any sweater, hat, jacket or scarf.
It measures 3" across, and it's made on a metal foundation.
It features my own lampwork glass beads, has accents of ric-rac and felt, seed beads and Czech glass and lucite beads.  It has a bar-style pin-back.

name: bauble necklace
description:
A set of graduated beads.  Made using all my favorite decorative techniques.  
This piece is 19" long, siting just below a medium-sized woman's collar bone.
The center bead is 3/4" in diameter.
Some beads are made from Effetre and some from Bullseye glass.  It's strung on two strands of heavy-gauge Softflex wire.
Please let me know if I can answer any other questions about this necklace.

name: elegant party earrings - pink
description:
Happy colors and a fancy, long shape. Fun as well as elegant.
They hang 3-3/4" from the top of the loop. 
Handmade glass beads, vintage beads, chain and parts, sterling beads & findings.

name: peace brooch
description:
This funky brooch will liven up your winter coat. 
It's made from a handmade cabachon, a ceramic bead, trade beads and seed beads and waxed linen. The findings are base metal, pad-and-post.
It measures 3" across, including the wisps.

name: veggie necklace
description:
Fresh from the garden!
Made from my handmade glass beads & buttons and seed beads.
The longest leek is 1-1/2" long and the total length of the necklace is 18-1/2".

name: peapod drops
description:
Detailed peapods to adorn your ears.
Made from my lampwork glass beads, seed beads and sterling findings.
They hang 2-3/8" long from the top of the loop.

name: striped hoops - pink & green
description:
These little lovelies are so simple and easy to wear.
The hoops are 5/8" in diameter and the total length, hoop and drop is 1-1/2" long.
The hoops are sterling silver.

name: happy colors knotted bracelet
description:
Happy ingredients make this a sweet bracelet - a starfish button, a bird, a flower, bright colored dots and stripes will carry you through the cold months ahead!
It is made from my handmade glass beads and button, as well as vintage glass beads, and is knotted with linen and floss.
It is for a 6-1/2" wrist, a medium-sized woman.

name: flower hoops - rose, coral, pale yellow
description:
So simple and easy to wear.
The hoops are 5/8" in diameter and the rose flowers are 7/8" in diameter.  
The hoops are sterling silver.

name: circus earrings - black
description:
So fun!
My least fragile and maybe, my funkiest style of earring.  They are strung on Soft Flex beading wire, making them flexible and almost indestructible. 
These drops are made from my handmade beads, vintage lucite beads, seed beads and sterling findings.  They hang 2-1/2" long from the top of the loop.

name: fancy flower hoops - red
description:
A more detailed version of my classic flower hoops. 
They are made from my handmade beads, accent beads and sterling findings. The pointy layer is lucite, so they are not fragile.
The hoops are 5/8" in diameter and the flowers are 1" in diameter.

name: flower toggle necklace
description:
An eclectic mix of materials, old and new: handmade glass beads, Indonesian trade beads, felt, resin, turquoise and and shell beads, seed beads and waxed linen. It's strung on super-strong Softflex.
17" around. 8-1/2" from the back to the center flower. The pendant section hangs 4-1/2" long.

name: winter roots necklace
description:
This is my favorite color-scheme right now!  (The colors of Amaryllis and Paper White bulbs - white roots, new-spring green and that rosey brown paper-like layer.)
Made from my lampwork glass beads and button, Indonesian trade beads, horn beads and seed beads. It is 23-1/2" in length.  Strung on Softflex.

name: long lantern drops
description:
These are signature Stephanie earrings.
They are made from my handmade glass beads, seed beads, vintage metal components and sterling beads and findings.
They measure 3-3/8" in length from the top of the loop.

name: yellow flower brooch
description:
The raddest, weirdest color combo, sure to liven up any sweater, hat, jacket or scarf.
It measures 1-5/8" across.
It features my own lampwork glass cabachon.  It has a pad-and-post closure.

name: striped hoops - turquoise, pink & gold
description:
These little lovelies are so simple and easy to wear.
The hoops are 5/8" in diameter and the total length, hoop and drop is 1-1/2" long.
The hoops are sterling silver.

name: flower necklace
description:
Subtle colors and neutral undertones. It will look marvelous on a solid-color dress, with T-shirt and jeans...and it easily dresses up or down.
This necklace is made from my own handmade glass beads, ceramic and shell beads, Czech glass beads and seed beads, floss and waxed linen.
It is 18" long, sitting on a medium-sized woman's collar bone.
Please let me know if I can answer any other questions about it.

name: flower hoops - purple & yellow
description:
Bright and bold, but also little and delicate.
The hoops are 5/8" and flower is 7/8" in diameter.
The hoops are sterling silver.

name: long flower drops - lavendar & aqua
description:
Delicate and kinetic.
Handmade glass beads, seed beads and sterling findings.
2-3/4" long from the top of the loop. Fragile.

name: happy little necklace
description:
Extremely wearable, simple strand of luscious beads. Spice up all your black clothes this winter.
It is 22" long and made from my handmade glass beads, a handmade button for a closure and glass accent beads.

name: lantern drop earrings
description:
Happy earrings that make the outfit. Easy to wear - a simple shape and light-in-weight. 
They hang 2-1/2" from the top of the wire.
Handmade glass beads, seed beads, vintage metal & silver beads, sterling silver findings.

name: blue bird earrings
description:
They measure 1-1/4" in length from the top of the loop and the birds are 1-1/4" long.
Handmade glass beads, seed beads and sterling findings.

name: Designing Jewelry with Glass Beads
description:
This is my book!  I hope you love it.  I would like to sign it for you.  Please indicate that wish upon check-out.
The book covers the history of glass beads, design and color perspectives and also contains reference and classification materials for the collector. There are fully-illustrated instructions for 20 projects, including the Spiny Knotted Bracelet and Necklace, several styles of funky earrings and many other brand new designs.
